condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Recruitment of external auditor | Description: The Recipient shall recruit, no later than six (6) months afterthe Effective Date, an independent external auditor for the Project in accordance with the provisions of Section III of Schedule 2to the Financing Agreement. | Due Date :
Finance Agreement: Designate, by no later than six months after effectiveness, a representative for the Regional CoordinationCommittee.

Finance Agreement: Update the project manual of procedures that will include FM and accounting aspects| Description: The Recipientshall ensure that the existing financial manual of procedures has been updated within 3 months after the effectiveness to take intoconsideration any specific concerns relating to this project. | Due Date :

Finance Agreement: Upgrading of existing Financial Management Software and fiduciary staff training | Description: The Recipientshall have upgraded the existing financial management software, no later than three (3) months after the Effective Date, in formand substance acceptable to the Association and included the procurement system (planning, monitoring and contract management) withthereto.
